		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I was looking to play the fallowing games:<br /><br />Earthbound 0<br />Final Fantasy 2-3<br />Fire Emblem: Shadow Dragon and the Blade of Light<br />Fire Emblem: Gaiden<br />Famicom Wars<br />Megami Tensei 1 &amp; 2<br /><br /><br />The first two I can find rerpos online, the last few I can't.   Has anyone else done them, and if I have to, what is the easiest way to do them myself.

		

		</td>
